<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <title>Hyperborea – Jornada Pokémon, Crônicas e Liga</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Hyperborea: crônicas de Pokémon, jornada OT I08S28, registros de coleção e projeto da Liga Hyperborea para 2027." />

  <!-- Ícones -->
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon.ico">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="192x192" href="/icon-192.png">
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="512x512" href="/icon-512.png">

  <style>
    :root{
      --hy-bg: #050b14;
      --hy-bg2: #07162a;
      --hy-panel: rgba(8, 18, 34, .88);
      --hy-panel2: rgba(12, 28, 52, .82);

      --hy-cyan: #20d3e6;
      --hy-blue: #3b82f6;
      --hy-violet: #6d4bd8;
      --hy-ice: #dff7ff;
      --hy-soft: #9fb9d1;
      --hy-text: #eef9ff;
      --hy-border: rgba(75, 184, 220, .28);
      --hy-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, .45);
    }

    *{ box-sizing: border-box; }

    html{
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body{
      margin: 0;
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
      color: var(--hy-text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 18% 0%, rgba(32, 211, 230, .14), transparent 36%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 92% 12%, rgba(59, 130, 246, .16), transparent 38%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 78% 90%, rgba(109, 75, 216, .16), transparent 42%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, #030812, #07162a 58%, #061a38);
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    a{
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    img{
      max-width: 100%;
      display: block;
    }

    /* ===== HEADER ===== */

    .hy-header{
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 30;
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      background: rgba(5, 11, 20, .78);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hy-border);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.22);
    }

    .hy-header-inner{
      max-width: 1160px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .hy-logo{
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .hy-logo img{
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border: 1px solid rgba(32,211,230,.35);
      box-shadow: 0 0 22px rgba(32,211,230,.20);
    }

    .hy-logo-text{
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .hy-logo-title{
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 950;
      letter-spacing: .08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .hy-logo-sub{
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--hy-soft);
    }

    .hy-nav{
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .hy-nav a{
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--hy-ice);
      border: 1px solid rgba(75,184,220,.28);
      background: rgba(8,18,34,.74);
      padding: 9px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      box-shadow:
        0 8px 18px rgba(0,0,0,.24),
        inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      transition: transform .15s ease-out, border-color .15s ease-out, background .15s ease-out;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .hy-nav a:hover{
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      border-color: rgba(32,211,230,.75);
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, rgba(32,211,230,.28), rgba(109,75,216,.28));
    }

    .hy-menu-toggle{
      display: none;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(32,211,230,.38);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 0 0, rgba(32,211,230,.38), transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 100% 100%, rgba(109,75,216,.38), transparent 60%),
        rgba(8,18,34,.92);
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(0,0,0,.34);
    }

    .hy-menu-bars{
      width: 18px;
      height: 12px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .hy-menu-bars span{
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 2px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--hy-cyan), var(--hy-violet));
      transition: transform .18s ease-out, opacity .18s ease-out, top .18s ease-out, bottom .18s ease-out;
    }

    .hy-menu-bars span:nth-child(1){ top: 0; }
    .hy-menu-bars span:nth-child(2){ top: 5px; }
    .hy-menu-bars span:nth-child(3){ bottom: 0; }

    .hy-menu-toggle.is-open .hy-menu-bars span:nth-child(1){
      top: 5px;
      transform: rotate(45deg);
    }

    .hy-menu-toggle.is-open .hy-menu-bars span:nth-child(2){
      opacity: 0;
    }

    .hy-menu-toggle.is-open .hy-menu-bars span:nth-child(3){
      bottom: 5px;
      transform: rotate(-45deg);
    }

    .hy-nav-mobile{
      position: absolute;
      top: 100%;
      right: 16px;
      margin-top: 8px;
      display: none;
      width: min(320px, calc(100vw - 32px));
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(75,184,220,.32);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 0 0, rgba(32,211,230,.14), transparent 55%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 100% 100%, rgba(109,75,216,.16), transparent 55%),
        rgba(5,11,20,.96);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 36px rgba(0,0,0,.38);
    }

    .hy-nav-mobile.is-open{
      display: block;
    }

    .hy-nav-mobile a{
      display: block;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 7px 0;
      padding: 11px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #ffffff;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 0 0, rgba(255,255,255,.18), transparent 55%),
        linear-gradient(120deg, var(--hy-cyan), var(--hy-blue), var(--hy-violet));
      box-shadow:
        0 12px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.34),
        inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.35);
    }

    /* ===== BASE ===== */

    main{
      max-width: 1160px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 18px 16px 28px;
    }

    .hy-kicker{
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .28em;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--hy-soft);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .hy-gradient-text{
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--hy-cyan), var(--hy-blue), var(--hy-violet));
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      color: transparent;
    }

    /* ===== HERO ===== */

    .hy-hero{
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 30px;
      border: 1px solid var(--hy-border);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 18% 0%, rgba(32,211,230,.18), transparent 48%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 92% 38%, rgba(109,75,216,.18), transparent 52%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(7,22,42,.92), rgba(4,9,18,.94));
      box-shadow: 0 26px 58px rgba(0,0,0,.36);
      padding: 28px 22px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.25fr .85fr;
      gap: 24px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hy-hero::before{
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: -2px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(32,211,230,.10), transparent),
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 110%, rgba(59,130,246,.16), transparent 42%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hy-hero > *{
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .hy-title{
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: clamp(32px, 6vw, 58px);
      line-height: 1.02;
      font-weight: 950;
      letter-spacing: -.055em;
    }

    .hy-hero-text{
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 66ch;
      color: #c7dced;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.85;
    }

    .hy-hero-actions{
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .hy-btn-main,
    .hy-btn-sec{
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 10px 17px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 900;
      transition: transform .15s ease-out, filter .15s ease-out, border-color .15s ease-out;
    }

    .hy-btn-main{
      color: #ffffff;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 0 0, rgba(255,255,255,.20), transparent 55%),
        linear-gradient(120deg, var(--hy-cyan), var(--hy-blue), var(--hy-violet));
      box-shadow:
        0 14px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.40),
        inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.32);
    }

    .hy-btn-sec{
      color: var(--hy-ice);
      border: 1px solid rgba(75,184,220,.38);
      background: rgba(8,18,34,.72);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 26px rgba(0,0,0,.25);
    }

    .hy-btn-main:hover,
    .hy-btn-sec:hover{
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      filter: brightness(1.07);
    }

    .hy-hero-panel{
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(75,184,220,.32);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 0 0, rgba(32,211,230,.12), transparent 55%),
        rgba(3, 8, 18, .58);
      padding: 18px 16px;
      box-shadow:
        0 18px 36px rgba(0,0,0,.32),
        inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    }

    .hy-hero-panel h3{
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 950;
    }

    .hy-hero-panel ul{
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 18px;
      color: #c7dced;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.9;
    }

    /* ===== BANNER ROTATIVO ===== */

    .hy-banner{
      margin: 24px 0 12px;
      border-radius: 26px;
      border: 1px solid var(--hy-border);
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 22px 50px rgba(0,0,0,.36);
      background: rgba(5,11,20,.88);
    }

    .hy-banner-inner{
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      padding-top: 41.666%;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hy-banner-track{
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      display: flex;
      transition: transform .5s ease-in-out;
    }

    .hy-banner-slide{
      flex: 0 0 100%;
      min-width: 100%;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 0 0, rgba(32,211,230,.16), transparent 55%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 100% 100%, rgba(109,75,216,.18), transparent 55%),
        #07162a;
    }

    .hy-banner-slide img{
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .hy-banner-dots{
      position: absolute;
      right: 16px;
      bottom: 14px;
      display: flex;
      gap: 7px;
      z-index: 5;
    }

    .hy-banner-dot{
      width: 9px;
      height: 9px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(223,247,255,.85);
      background: rgba(5,11,20,.82);
      opacity: .78;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: width .2s ease, background .2s ease, opacity .2s ease;
    }

    .hy-banner-dot.is-active{
      width: 22px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--hy-cyan), var(--hy-violet));
      opacity: 1;
    }

    /* ===== SEÇÕES ===== */

    .hy-section{
      padding: 40px 0 12px;
    }

    .hy-section-header{
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 auto 24px;
    }

    .hy-section-title{
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(24px, 4vw, 34px);
      line-height: 1.1;
      font-weight: 950;
      letter-spacing: -.04em;
    }

    .hy-section-sub{
      margin: 9px auto 0;
      color: #b8ccdc;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .hy-grid-3{
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .hy-card{
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid var(--hy-border);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 0 0, rgba(32,211,230,.10), transparent 55%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 100% 100%, rgba(109,75,216,.12), transparent 55%),
        rgba(8,18,34,.74);
      box-shadow:
        0 18px 38px rgba(0,0,0,.24),
        inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.06);
      padding: 18px 16px;
    }

    .hy-card-mark{
      width: 38px;
      height: 38px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 950;
      font-size: 13px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 0 0, rgba(255,255,255,.22), transparent 55%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, var(--hy-cyan), var(--hy-blue), var(--hy-violet));
      box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.30);
    }

    .hy-card h3{
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.2;
      font-weight: 950;
    }

    .hy-card p{
      margin: 0;
      color: #c7dced;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .hy-card ul{
      margin: 12px 0 0;
      padding-left: 18px;
      color: #c7dced;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    /* ===== BLOCO JORNADA ===== */

    .hy-feature{
      border-radius: 28px;
      border: 1px solid var(--hy-border);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 0 0, rgba(32,211,230,.14), transparent 58%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 100% 100%, rgba(109,75,216,.16), transparent 58%),
        rgba(8,18,34,.78);
      padding: 22px 18px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.1fr) minmax(0, .9fr);
      gap: 20px;
      align-items: center;
      box-shadow: 0 22px 46px rgba(0,0,0,.28);
    }

    .hy-feature h2{
      margin: 0 0 9px;
      font-size: clamp(24px, 4vw, 34px);
      line-height: 1.12;
      letter-spacing: -.04em;
    }

    .hy-feature p{
      margin: 0;
      color: #c7dced;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.85;
    }

    .hy-stats{
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .hy-stat{
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(75,184,220,.28);
      background: rgba(3,8,18,.42);
      padding: 13px 14px;
    }

    .hy-stat strong{
      display: block;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--hy-ice);
      margin-bottom: 3px;
    }

    .hy-stat span{
      display: block;
      color: #b8ccdc;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ===== INFRA ===== */

    .hy-infra{
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .hy-infra-card{
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid var(--hy-border);
      background: rgba(8,18,34,.74);
      padding: 18px 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 38px rgba(0,0,0,.24);
    }

    .hy-infra-card h3{
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 17px;
    }

    .hy-infra-card p{
      margin: 0;
      color: #c7dced;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .hy-code{
      display: inline-flex;
      margin-top: 12px;
      padding: 8px 10px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(75,184,220,.28);
      background: rgba(3,8,18,.58);
      color: var(--hy-ice);
      font-size: 12px;
      word-break: break-all;
    }

    /* ===== FINAL ===== */

    .hy-call{
      margin: 42px 0 22px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(75,184,220,.32);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 0 0, rgba(32,211,230,.18), transparent 58%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 100% 100%, rgba(109,75,216,.22), transparent 58%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(7,22,42,.95), rgba(5,11,20,.95));
      box-shadow: 0 24px 52px rgba(0,0,0,.34);
      padding: 22px 18px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.3fr) minmax(0, .8fr);
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hy-call h2{
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 950;
      letter-spacing: -.04em;
    }

    .hy-call p{
      margin: 0;
      color: #c7dced;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .hy-call-actions{
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .hy-disclaimer{
      max-width: 920px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      color: #7f99ad;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      padding: 12px 0 4px;
    }

    footer{
      border-top: 1px solid var(--hy-border);
      background: rgba(5,11,20,.76);
    }

    .hy-footer-inner{
      max-width: 1160px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 16px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #b8ccdc;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    /* ===== RESPONSIVO ===== */

    @media (max-width: 920px){
      .hy-nav{
        display: none;
      }

      .hy-menu-toggle{
        display: inline-flex;
      }

      .hy-hero,
      .hy-feature,
      .hy-call{
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .hy-grid-3,
      .hy-infra{
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px){
      main{
        padding: 14px 14px 24px;
      }

      .hy-hero{
        padding: 24px 16px;
        border-radius: 26px;
      }

      .hy-title{
        font-size: clamp(31px, 12vw, 46px);
      }

      .hy-logo-title{
        font-size: 12px;
      }

      .hy-logo-sub{
        display: none;
      }

      .hy-hero-actions .hy-btn-main,
      .hy-hero-actions .hy-btn-sec,
      .hy-call-actions .hy-btn-main,
      .hy-call-actions .hy-btn-sec{
        width: 100%;
      }

      .hy-banner-inner{
        padding-top: 62%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <!-- CABEÇALHO -->
  <header class="hy-header">
    <div class="hy-header-inner">
      <a href="/index.html" class="hy-logo">
        <img src="/assets/hyperborea-logo.png" alt="Logo Hyperborea">
        <span class="hy-logo-text">
          <span class="hy-logo-title">Hyperborea</span>
          <span class="hy-logo-sub">Jornada, crônicas e liga</span>
        </span>
      </a>

      <nav class="hy-nav">
        <a href="#cronicas">Crônicas</a>
        <a href="#liga">Liga 2027</a>
        <a href="#jornada">Jornada OT</a>
        <a href="#infra">GitHub × Vercel</a>
        <a href="#comunidade">Comunidade</a>
      </nav>

      <button class="hy-menu-toggle" type="button" aria-label="Abrir menu">
        <div class="hy-menu-bars">
          <span></span><span></span><span></span>
        </div>
      </button>
    </div>

    <nav class="hy-nav-mobile" id="hy-nav-mobile">
      <a href="#cronicas">Crônicas</a>
      <a href="#liga">Liga 2027</a>
      <a href="#jornada">Jornada OT</a>
      <a href="#infra">GitHub × Vercel</a>
      <a href="#comunidade">Comunidade</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main id="topo">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="hy-hero">
      <div>
        <div class="hy-kicker">HYPERBOREA • ARQUIVO VIVO</div>

        <h1 class="hy-title">
          Jornada Pokémon, crônicas e comunidade em <span class="hy-gradient-text">continuidade</span>.
        </h1>

        <p class="hy-hero-text">
          A Hyperborea nasce como um espaço de registro, memória e organização da jornada Pokémon:
          crônicas, conquistas, coleção, trajetória OT, projeto de liga e comunidade para quem valoriza
          presença, autenticidade e continuidade.
        </p>

        <div class="hy-hero-actions">
          <a href="#cronicas" class="hy-btn-main">Ver crônicas</a>
          <a href="#jornada" class="hy-btn-sec">Jornada OT I08S28</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="hy-hero-panel">
        <h3>O que esta página reúne</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Crônicas de Pokémon e registros de jornada;</li>
          <li>Liga Hyperborea / Champions 2027 em desenvolvimento;</li>
          <li>Jornada OT Pokémon I08S28;</li>
          <li>estrutura técnica em GitHub + Vercel;</li>
          <li>pontes futuras com Instagram e grupo WhatsApp.</li>
        </ul>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <!-- BANNERS -->
    <section class="hy-banner" aria-label="Banners Hyperborea">
      <div class="hy-banner-inner" id="hy-banner-inner">
        <div class="hy-banner-track" id="hy-banner-track">

          <a href="#apresentacao" class="hy-banner-slide">
            <img src="/assets/banner01-hyperborea-apresentacao.png" alt="Banner de apresentação da Hyperborea">
          </a>

          <a href="#instagram" class="hy-banner-slide">
            <img src="/assets/banner02-hyperborea-instagram.png" alt="Banner do Instagram da Hyperborea">
          </a>

          <a href="#whatsapp" class="hy-banner-slide">
            <img src="/assets/banner03-hyperborea-whatsapp.png" alt="Banner do grupo WhatsApp da Hyperborea">
